The '''''Journal of Archaeological Science''''' is a [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] that covers "the development and application of scientific techniques and methodologies to all areas of [[archaeology]]".<ref>{{cite web|title=Journal of Archaeological Science|url=http://www.journals.elsevier.com/journal-of-archaeological-science/|work=Elsevier.com|publisher=Elsevier|accessdate=16 December 2011}}</ref> The journal was established in 1974 and is published by [[Academic Press]], an imprint of [[Elsevier]].

==  Abstracting and indexing ==
The journal is abstracted or indexed in:<ref>{{cite web|title=Journal of Archaeological Science|url=https://ulrichsweb.serialssolutions.com/title/1324066159933/60970|work=Ulrichsweb|publisher=ProQuest|accessdate=16 December 2011}}</ref>

